Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,十九世纪中叶\N{\ren}China in the mid-19th century...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,清廷腐败 民不聊生\N{\ren}the suffering of its people under the corrupt rule of the Qing dynasty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太平军义举反清\N{\ren}set the stage for the Taiping Rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,中国陷入长达十四年的内战\N{\ren}During the chaos of the 14 years long civil war,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,造成死亡人口近七千万\N{\ren}70 million people died in battle or from starvation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这个数字是第二次世界大战全球死亡人口的总和\N{\ren}The casualties equaled the recorded death toll from WWII.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他说\N{\ren}He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那天从死人堆里爬出来\N{\ren}the day he crawled out from the pile of corpses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\ren}he was a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他还说\N{\ren}He also said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个年代 死 很容易\N{\ren}it was an age when death came easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,活着的 更难\N{\ren}but living was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人都死光了\N{\ren}All my men died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就剩我一个\N{\ren}I alone survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你命好\N{\ren}You were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我装死的\N{\ren}I played dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟 一千六百多人\N{\ren}My brothers... more than 1600 men...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拼了三天三夜\N{\ren}fought for three days and nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,都没了\N{\ren}They all died...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营那帮畜生\N{\ren}The Kui army were inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只站在后面 一动不动\N{\ren}They only stood behind us and watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我那帮兄弟就这样一个一个的\N{\ren}My brothers were slaughtered one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都没了\N{\ren}No one survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 那天他遇到了一个女人\N{\ren}He met a woman that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在废弃的破屋里过了一夜\N{\ren}They spent the night in a deserted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不知是那碗粥 还是那个女人\N{\ren}He didn't know if it was the woman or the soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让他感觉 原来他还活着\N{\ren}that brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿有饭吃啊\N{\ren}Where can I find food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去大街破房子前蹲着\N{\ren}Try the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他说\N{\ren}He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次碰到我的那天\N{\ren}the first time he met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,天是灰蒙蒙的 跟他的心情一样\N{\ren}the sky was overcast, like his mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可我清楚地记得\N{\ren}But I remember clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那天是个晴天 阳光刺眼\N{\ren}that it was a glaringly sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完就跟我去干玩命的活\N{\ren}Eat your food and let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完 干活\N{\ren}Eat and get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抢啊\N{\ren}Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么能打 跟我\N{\ren}You sure know how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你见大哥\N{\ren}I should introduce you to my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么活\N{\ren}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,打劫\N{\ren}To rob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,劫军粮\N{\ren}From the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他后来说 你们胆大包天\N{\ren}He later told me he was outraged...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢抢军队的粮食\N{\ren}that bandits like us dared steal from troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 方圆百里已无粮\N{\ren}What did we care? Famine is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,饿都饿死了 管他谁的粮\N{\ren}We either robbed or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,冲出去\N{\ren}Ride out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快 杀那个领头的\N{\ren}Seize their leader, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 他不但救了我\N{\ren}He saved my life that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在教我\N{\ren}and taught me a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,打蛇打七寸 擒贼先擒王\N{\ren}Strike the head... and the body will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳哥\N{\ren}Brother Jiang...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\ren}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个人给的\N{\ren}That man gave them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是将军穿的\N{\ren}They're for generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳哥做将军了\N{\ren}Brother Jiang has become a general!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳哥做将军了\N{\ren}Brother Jiang has become a general!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\ren}What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想家\N{\ren}My home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\N{\ren}They've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别急 跟上 跟上 有的吃啦\N{\ren}Come with me! We've got food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天晚上在这里大吃一顿\N{\ren}I have good news, tonight we feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么一个人呢\N{\ren}Why are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是从家里头跑出来的\N{\ren}I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,听口音 你是扬州人\N{\ren}Is that a Yangzhou accent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你听出来啦\N{\ren}You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还能听出我是扬州口音啊\N{\ren}How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你听过扬州瘦马吗\N{\ren}Have you ever heard of Yangzhou Ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是找些漂亮的小女孩 教她们琴棋书画\N{\ren}You mean pretty young girls who are trained as courtesans...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,养大了以后卖给富人做妾 是吧\N{\ren}and sold to rich men?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不过\N{\ren}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我十五岁那年\N{\ren}But when I turned 15...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,刚要被卖出去\N{\ren}and was about to be sold...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候带我一起玩的朋友\N{\ren}a man came and stole me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就把我给抢回来了\N{\ren}He was my childhood playmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他还杀了人\N{\ren}He killed a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就带我躲进山里做了匪\N{\ren}We went into hiding and he became a bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他不知道你已经变了\N{\ren}He thought he saved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为救了你\N{\ren}but you were no longer the same peasant girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他是好人\N{\ren}He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安心上路\N{\ren}Go in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,安心上路\N{\ren}Go in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥定的规矩\N{\ren}Big brother laid down the rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,留下空位斟满酒\N{\ren}to save seats and wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,敬死去的兄弟\N{\ren}for the brothers who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在军中是个头\N{\ren}Were you a general in the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的事了\N{\ren}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为何离开\N{\ren}Why did you desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来 喝\N{\ren}Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是朝廷的兵\N{\ren}My troops and the Kui troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,约好联手消灭敌军\N{\ren}planned to join forces against the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营出尔反尔\N{\ren}But they betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,寡不敌众\N{\ren}We were outnumbered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟就这样死光了\N{\ren}and all my brothers were killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天大地大 没有兄弟情大\N{\ren}There's nothing more important than the love between brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\ren}That I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这年头没有兄弟\N{\ren}These days, without brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,活不下去\N{\ren}you can't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳 吃饭了\N{\ren}Wu-Yang, dinner's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,新招回村的人都会留下吗\N{\ren}Are the new recruits staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有饭吃 谁不留下\N{\ren}No one wants to leave when there's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 来了一个姓庞的 很厉害\N{\ren}Except for Pang, he's not our kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他走不走 我就不知道了\N{\ren}I don't know if he's staying or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮吧\N{\ren}Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,死人身上捡的\N{\ren}I snatched it from a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你晓得这是什么吗\N{\ren}Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保平安的\N{\ren}It protects you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚是真的吗\N{\ren}Did that night really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直等在那儿\N{\ren}I waited there for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为是梦\N{\ren}wondering if it was all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,既然跑了 干嘛还回来\N{\ren}If you ran away, why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,跑了很多次了\N{\ren}I ran away many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想得挺好\N{\ren}had it all thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都是回来\N{\ren}But I always ended up back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛还回来呢\N{\ren}Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的命 该自己做主\N{\ren}You should decide for your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在这儿\N{\ren}Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“魁”\N{\ren}"Kui".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛抢我们粮食\N{\ren}Why are you robbing our food?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿个破铁棍子杵我\N{\ren}I dare you to hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你杵啊 你杵啊\N{\ren}Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\ren}Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你几岁啊 我当你奶奶都成\N{\ren}I'm old enough to be your grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再动我就开枪了 要死人的\N{\ren}Stand back or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕你\N{\ren}I dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的要开枪 我真的要\N{\ren}I swear I'll shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕死 你打死我吧\N{\ren}Go ahead! Kill me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\ren}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都别动\N{\ren}Nobody moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不看着我\N{\ren}Look at me when I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为抢了粮车 粮食就归你了吗\N{\ren}You think you can keep the food you robbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而今是给你们个机会 报效朝廷\N{\ren}Consider this as a pay back to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们有枪 就跟他们拼了\N{\ren}If only we had guns... we could fight them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.87,0:23:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那是送死\N{\ren}That's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这么活着 还不如死\N{\ren}I'd rather die than live like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当匪 狗的命 永远被人追\N{\ren}Thieves are always on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不投军\N{\ren}Why not join the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,投了军有军饷\N{\ren}Once you're in the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有了军饷 就可以买粮食养家糊口\N{\ren}you'll receive wages to feed your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,投了军有枪炮\N{\ren}You'll get guns so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有了枪炮 就没人敢欺负我们了\N{\ren}that no one will bully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这村子才真的太平\N{\ren}This village will finally have peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是土匪 朝廷能收我们吗\N{\ren}We're bandits, will the army take us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.34,0:24:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营嚣张 势大力强\N{\ren}The Kui army is grandiose and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这点儿人 他们根本看不上\N{\ren}They couldn't care less about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是的军机处的陈公 正缺人手\N{\ren}But Lord Chen's army is desperate for men.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他的绿营兵常被魁字营欺负\N{\ren}He wants to increase his power...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.37,0:24:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想壮大势力\N{\ren}to rival the Kui army.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们投他 那正是雪中送炭\N{\ren}He should welcome us with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎 抓住这个机会\N{\ren}Er-Hu , use this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.67,0:24:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让今天的事 永远不要再发生\N{\ren}Then today's event... will never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.44,0:24:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当匪\N{\ren}As bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要当最大的\N{\ren}We have to be the biggest!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.07,0:25:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前是清军\N{\ren}You deserted the Qing army,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现下带我们投军 不黑不白的\N{\ren}now you want us to join them? You're a two-faced man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.31,0:25:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,凭什么信你\N{\ren}Why shall we trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,纳投名状\N{\ren}Take the blood oath!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.91,0:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟结义 各杀一个外人\N{\ren}To be blood brothers, we kill an outsider...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.71,0:25:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,断绝后路 以示忠诚\N{\ren}to show our loyalty to the brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.21,0:25:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,从此 兄弟的命是命\N{\ren}Only the lives of our brothers count.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.77,0:25:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的皆可杀\N{\ren}The rest are expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.61,0:25:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我问他\N{\ren}I asked him that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.44,0:25:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,纳了投名状 永远没有退路\N{\ren}There's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.21,0:25:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意吗\N{\ren}Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.34,0:25:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他没吭声\N{\ren}He said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.74,0:25:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要\N{\ren}Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.64,0:25:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷 怎么回事啊\N{\ren}Masters, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.91,0:25:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,狗日的 你干什么啊 没招你们没惹你们的\N{\ren}What are you bastards doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.11,0:25:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要杀我们啊\N{\ren}What did we do wrong?...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.07,0:25:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是从你们村路过吗\N{\ren}We were only passing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷 求求你 放 放了我吧\N{\ren}Have mercy on me... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.71,0:26:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,记住我这张脸\N{\ren}Remember my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下回投胎找我报仇\N{\ren}and take revenge in your next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.37,0:26:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今有庞青云\N{\ren}We, Pang Qing-Yun,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.14,0:26:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,赵二虎\N{\ren}Zhao Er-Hu,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.04,0:26:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,姜午阳\N{\ren}and Jiang Wu-Yang...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.41,0:26:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,纳投名状 结兄弟义\N{\ren}join the brotherhood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.84,0:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,死生相托 吉凶相救\N{\ren}We take the blood oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.27,0:26:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,福祸相依 患难相扶\N{\ren}We pledge our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.07,0:26:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,外人乱我兄弟者\N{\ren}Those who bring us harm...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,视投名状 必杀之\N{\ren}must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.41,0:26:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟乱我兄弟者\N{\ren}A brother who harms another brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.27,0:26:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,视投名状 必杀之\N{\ren}must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.81,0:26:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天地作证 山河为盟\N{\ren}Heaven and earth bear witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有违此誓 天地诛之\N{\ren}and strike dead any man who breaks his oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.51,0:26:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,人和一心\N{\ren}We share one heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.04,0:26:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他后来跟我说\N{\ren}He told me later that...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.77,0:26:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他不相信投名状\N{\ren}he didn't believe in the pledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.61,0:26:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我问 那你信什么\N{\ren}I asked him what he believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.64,0:26:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他相信二哥\N{\ren}He said Er-Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我\N{\ren}and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.14,0:27:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等一会儿 把这鞋带上\N{\ren}Wait! Take these shoes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.61,0:27:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,路上要小心啊\N{\ren}Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.84,0:27:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,以后娘再也看不见你了\N{\ren}Mother may never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.94,0:27:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 我走了\N{\ren}Good-bye, ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.81,0:27:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎哥\N{\ren}Er Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.61,0:27:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,石锦标带着一群人走了\N{\ren}Shi and his men are leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.77,0:27:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就留下一句话\N{\ren}He said that he'd rather die...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,说誓死也不投清兵\N{\ren}than serve the Qing army!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.34,0:28:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你带一营兵\N{\ren}Your entire battalion perished...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.61,0:28:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在鹤川伏击太平军\N{\ren}in the battle against the Taiping rebels in Hechuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然全军覆没\N{\ren}and you disappeared for 2 months!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.54,0:28:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,两个月没见 还敢回来\N{\ren}How dare you return now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.91,0:28:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,陈大人\N{\ren}My Lord Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.04,0:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤川一战\N{\ren}Lord Jiang sent the Kui army...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.24,0:28:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,姜大人派魁字营在我左翼护守\N{\ren}to aid us in the battle at the Hechuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.51,0:28:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁临阵畏敌退兵三十里\N{\ren}But they left us to fend for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一营的兄弟就这样眼睁睁的死光了\N{\ren}My men were slaughtered on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:28:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,全军覆没\N{\ren}All your men died...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.07,0:29:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一人活着\N{\ren}but you alone survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不死\N{\ren}I stayed alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.51,0:29:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是要回来见你\N{\ren}just to see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.84,0:29:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,姜大人\N{\ren}Lord Jiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.11,0:29:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个人啊\N{\ren}How many men do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.14,0:29:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,八百\N{\ren}800.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.24,0:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我八百\N{\ren}Give me another 800...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,十五日之内 我攻下舒城\N{\ren}and I will capture Shu City within 15 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.57,0:29:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,军中无戏言\N{\ren}Don't jest with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.01,0:29:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,十日\N{\ren}10!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.74,0:29:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,十日攻下舒城\N{\ren}I will capture Shu City in 10 days !
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.14,0:29:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\ren}then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.47,0:29:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我再给你一千五百精兵\N{\ren}I'll give you 1,500 fine soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.37,0:29:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有军饷\N{\ren}but no wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.54,0:29:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要军饷\N{\ren}We don't need wages;
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.24,0:29:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,攻下城 一半的东西归我们\N{\ren}we get half the spoils once we capture Shu City.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.87,0:29:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang Qing-Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.41,0:29:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你字“鹿山” 就叫“山字营”吧\N{\ren}Name your army "Shan".
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.14,0:29:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢三位大人\N{\ren}Thank you, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.24,0:30:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在赌\N{\ren}You're gambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.21,0:30:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拿八百条人命在赌\N{\ren}with 800 lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.37,0:30:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,打仗本身就是赌\N{\ren}War is a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.01,0:30:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不赌\N{\ren}I won't gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这一千五百兵 是陈公的家底\N{\ren}My 1500 men are the last of Lord Chen's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.97,0:30:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,打没了\N{\ren}If we lose them...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.27,0:30:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,陈公在朝廷说话就没底气\N{\ren}my lord will be powerless at the imperial court.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.27,0:30:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何才肯出手\N{\ren}Make me an offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兵\N{\ren}My army...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.17,0:30:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只给你壮声势\N{\ren}will only give you a semblance of multitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.71,0:30:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你唯一可以赢的机会\N{\ren}This is your only chance for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.61,0:30:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不然\N{\ren}Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.67,0:30:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营永远都把你踩在脚下\N{\ren}you'll forever be at the mercy of the Kui army!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.21,0:30:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.81,0:30:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,都是坏的\N{\ren}They're all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.24,0:31:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对面有两百枝洋枪\N{\ren}We'll be facing 200 rifles.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.47,0:31:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,仗很难打\N{\ren}The odds are against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.17,0:31:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要赢 只有一个办法\N{\ren}To win, we need to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.74,0:31:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,豁出去 破他们的枪阵\N{\ren}Break through their firing line...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,贴过去 跟他们斗狠\N{\ren}Engage them in hand to hand combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.40,0:31:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们\N{\ren}Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他 谁最狠\N{\ren}Tell him who's the toughest?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.44,0:31:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我最狠\N{\ren}We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.07,0:31:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,两军相隔三百大步\N{\ren}The enemy will be 300 paces away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.84,0:31:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,火枪的射程是两百步\N{\ren}Rifles have a range of 200 paces...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.40,0:31:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,弓箭只有一百步\N{\ren}arrows have only 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.67,0:31:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要两百个兄弟冲在前面\N{\ren}We'll need a vanguard of 200 men...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.27,0:31:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,弓箭手紧跟其后 再冲两百\N{\ren}to run straight at the firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.84,0:31:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,听见枪声不要躲 继续冲\N{\ren}They must not dodge the bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.94,0:31:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命的贴上去\N{\ren}but must use their bodies as shields...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.30,0:31:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为弓箭手\N{\ren}so that our archers...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.74,0:31:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,赢得这一百步\N{\ren}who run behind them can get within range.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很多兄弟会死\N{\ren}Many brothers will die in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.07,0:31:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\ren}I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.81,0:32:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁跟我去\N{\ren}Who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.24,0:32:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意去的有安家费 死了两份\N{\ren}Die and your family will receive double your wages!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.57,0:32:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,活下来三份\N{\ren}Live and you receive triple!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.67,0:32:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能发财还不去呀\N{\ren}Don't you want to be rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.17,0:32:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是爷们就放个响屁\N{\ren}Where are the real men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.84,0:32:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 豁出去了\N{\ren}Damn it, count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去\N{\ren}Me too, I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.64,0:32:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,算我一个 我去\N{\ren}Count me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.47,0:32:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去\N{\ren}me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.07,0:32:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 我也去\N{\ren}I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.64,0:32:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,进舒城\N{\ren}Take Shu City!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.61,0:32:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抢钱 抢粮 抢娘们\N{\ren}Take their money, their food, their women!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.71,0:32:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,进舒城\N{\ren}Take Shu City!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.64,0:32:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抢钱 抢粮 抢娘们\N{\ren}Take their money, their food, their women!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.84,0:32:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抢钱 抢粮 抢娘们\N{\ren}Take their money, their food, their women!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抢钱 抢粮 抢娘们\N{\ren}Take their money, their food, their women!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.74,0:33:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,寡众悬殊\N{\ren}You're vastly outnumbered...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,胜负已分 天恩浩荡\N{\ren}victory is already ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.94,0:33:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,投降便可免你一死\N{\ren}Surrender and your life will be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.14,0:33:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.34,0:34:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\ren}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.77,0:34:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.07,0:34:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\ren}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.84,0:35:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\ren}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.77,0:35:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放\N{\ren}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.71,0:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.94,0:35:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快死光了 还不去\N{\ren}They're dying out there! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.57,0:35:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我记住\N{\ren}Shut up and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.51,0:35:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,战场上只有一个是头\N{\ren}There's only one commander in a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.37,0:35:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.87,0:35:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放箭\N{\ren}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.94,0:36:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,放 放箭\N{\ren}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.37,0:36:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哥\N{\ren}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.27,0:37:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥\N{\ren}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.84,0:37:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,预备\N{\ren}Prepare!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.27,0:37:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,蒙马眼\N{\ren}Blinders on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.51,0:38:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在用命 逼我出手\N{\ren}He's using himself to goad me into combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.14,0:40:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,冲\N{\ren}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.91,0:40:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,救大哥\N{\ren}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.87,0:41:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.34,0:41:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拔 不要拔出来\N{\ren}No! Don't pull that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧\N{\ren}Hold steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.24,0:42:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是真的要死在这里了\N{\ren}We're really going to die this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.04,0:42:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们纳了投名状\N{\ren}We're blood brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.11,0:42:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不求同生 但求同死\N{\ren}We die as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\ren}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.37,0:42:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,死也要拉个垫背的\N{\ren}We might as well take a few with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,杀一个算一个\N{\ren}as we go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.34,0:42:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,冲出去\N{\ren}Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.64,0:42:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.64,0:42:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,疯子\N{\ren}It's madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.31,0:42:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,八百人居然把五千人给搅乱了\N{\ren}800 men manage to upset an army of 5000...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.11,0:42:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有得打\N{\ren}We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.44,0:42:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太需要一场胜利了\N{\ren}We really need a victory badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.24,0:42:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我 冲\N{\ren}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.11,0:43:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳\N{\ren}Wu-Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.31,0:43:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳\N{\ren}Wu-Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.67,0:44:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,狄大人\N{\ren}Lord Di...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.01,0:45:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云也算是个福将啊\N{\ren}Pang Qing-Yun must be blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.84,0:45:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.91,0:45:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咱俩也算是有缘份\N{\ren}Fate has brought us together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.77,0:45:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,算你押宝押中了\N{\ren}How fortunate of you to capture Shu City...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.34,0:45:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舒城一战闯出了个名堂\N{\ren}you have made a name for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.61,0:45:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.11,0:45:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再给你五个营的兵力 怎么样\N{\ren}how does 5 more battalions sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.74,0:45:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我再锦上添花\N{\ren}On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.01,0:45:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,陆大山 在\N{\ren}Lu Da-Shan... Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.11,0:45:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今后归你调谴\N{\ren}will be under your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.24,0:45:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢大人\N{\ren}Thank you, My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.14,0:45:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang Qing-Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.04,0:45:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有个魁字营的老朋友在等你\N{\ren}Your old friend from the Kui army is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.47,0:45:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁\N{\ren}He Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.24,0:45:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在\N{\ren}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.57,0:45:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,参见大人\N{\ren}Greetings, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.94,0:45:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,庞将军 久违了\N{\ren}It's been a long time, General Pang.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.14,0:45:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是老交情\N{\ren}It'll be a reunion of old allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.77,0:45:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那就继续联手\N{\ren}with you leading the attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.17,0:45:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你攻城他接防\N{\ren}and him bringing up the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.24,0:45:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了 我们怎么分\N{\ren}How do we divide the spoils?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.87,0:45:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,狄大人\N{\ren}Lord Di and...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.21,0:45:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,陈大人\N{\ren}Lord Chen...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.74,0:45:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有意见吧\N{\ren}no objections I trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.44,0:45:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕他跑得太慢追不上\N{\ren}I'm afraid he won't be able to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.51,0:45:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,先取苏州再打南京 怎样\N{\ren}We'll take Suzhou, and then Nanking!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.94,0:46:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们笑什么\N{\ren}What are they laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.74,0:46:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,南京是敌人的心脏\N{\ren}Nanking is the enemy's capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.41,0:46:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欲破南京 先取苏州\N{\ren}To topple Nanking, we must first take Suzhou.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.67,0:46:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,仗打完了 他们赚什么\N{\ren}Since they have nothing to gain when the war is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.81,0:46:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是不会让我们打苏州的\N{\ren}they won't let us take Suzhou.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.84,0:46:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们打他们管得了吗\N{\ren}If we attack, they can't stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.07,0:46:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,安插魁字营\N{\ren}The Kui army was precisely sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.47,0:46:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了监视我们\N{\ren}to keep an eye on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.07,0:46:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快来呀 他们回来了\N{\ren}They've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.67,0:47:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小五\N{\ren}Xiao-Wu
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.01,0:47:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小五\N{\ren}Xiao-Wu, Xiao-Wu...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.64,0:47:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小五的鞋\N{\ren}Xiao-Wu's shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.14,0:47:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小五\N{\ren}Xiao-Wu...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.64,0:47:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小七\N{\ren}Xiao-Qi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.71,0:47:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小七 我的儿啊\N{\ren}Xiao-Qi... my boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.04,0:47:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不再是土匪\N{\ren}We were no longer bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.71,0:48:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 土匪只为自己兄弟去杀人\N{\ren}He said a bandit kills for his own interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.61,0:48:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而英雄却可以为别人牺牲\N{\ren}But a hero sacrifices for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.37,0:48:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当英雄\N{\ren}I wanted to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.64,0:48:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你瘦了\N{\ren}You've lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.17,0:48:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥说 这一走三年就回来\N{\ren}Big brother says, we'll only be away for 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.01,0:48:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不喜欢这里\N{\ren}I know you've never liked it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.01,0:48:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等打完了仗\N{\ren}When the war is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.14,0:48:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去一个好地方过日子\N{\ren}I'll find us a better place to settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.57,0:48:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那大哥呢\N{\ren}Where's Brother Pang?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.84,0:48:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在村外睡 他说不进来了\N{\ren}He's staying outside the village tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.81,0:48:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天一早就出发\N{\ren}We'll leave tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.41,0:50:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,记住\N{\ren}Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.74,0:50:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,兵不厌诈\N{\ren}Winning is all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.27,0:50:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\N{\ren}Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.91,0:50:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.64,0:50:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,进城接防\N{\ren}We're here to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.51,0:50:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让兄弟们逍遥三天\N{\ren}Give the men 3 days leave to pillage!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.97,0:50:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抢钱 抢粮 抢娘们\N{\ren}Let them take money, food and women!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.11,0:51:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,出来呀 仗已经打完了\N{\ren}You can come out now, the war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.37,0:51:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,出来呀\N{\ren}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.61,0:51:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧 别害怕\N{\ren}Come, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.74,0:51:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没吃东西吧\N{\ren}Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.57,0:51:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没吃东西吧\N{\ren}Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.57,0:51:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,饿不饿\N{\ren}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.81,0:51:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 你们干嘛\N{\ren}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.17,0:51:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干嘛 小姐\N{\ren}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.24,0:51:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看什么看 快搭把手啊\N{\ren}Don't just stay there! Give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.31,0:51:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\ren}No!...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.54,0:52:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 别过来\N{\ren}Don't touch me!...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.34,0:52:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,狗子 我走了啊\N{\ren}Gouzi, I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.47,0:52:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\ren}Let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.41,0:52:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大哥\N{\ren}Brother Pang.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.11,0:52:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,走 干嘛\N{\ren}Move! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.54,0:52:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们凭什么抓我\N{\ren}Why am I being arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.51,0:52:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走 怎么啦\N{\ren}Go! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.74,0:52:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,召集百姓 就地正法\N{\ren}Gather the people for a public execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.31,0:52:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎哥\N{\ren}Brother Zhao!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.14,0:52:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 怎么了\N{\ren}Brother, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.01,0:52:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奸淫民女\N{\ren}They raped 2 women.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.51,0:52:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进城抢三天 这是规矩\N{\ren}They were given three days of pillage, this was bound to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.67,0:52:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起这种事不能在我们的军队里发生\N{\ren}From this day on, I will not tolerate such conduct under my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.81,0:52:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直都是这样的呀\N{\ren}It's what we've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.41,0:52:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是匪 今天是兵\N{\ren}We're soldiers now, not bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.01,0:52:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,匪气不改 什么也做不成\N{\ren}We must better ourselves or we won't achieve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.97,0:53:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们这样做\N{\ren}If we allow this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.27,0:53:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,跟魁字营那班畜生有什么区别\N{\ren}we're no better than those Kui bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.34,0:53:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,规矩总有开始的一天 就是今天\N{\ren}Today is the day we start setting down some rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.87,0:53:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚杀了那些女人的家里人\N{\ren}We've just killed their families!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.24,0:53:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了她们的家\N{\ren}Now you want to protect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.54,0:53:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你现下反过来保护他们\N{\ren}By killing our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.24,0:53:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那以后有谁来帮你卖命\N{\ren}No one will risk their lives fighting for you after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.64,0:53:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.61,0:53:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的吧 你看他们\N{\ren}Listen to me, look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.94,0:53:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们懂了\N{\ren}They've learned their lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.27,0:53:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着杀头的嘛 对不对\N{\ren}There's no need to kill them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.11,0:53:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么\N{\ren}Don't just kneel there!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.47,0:53:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快说你们认错\N{\ren}Say you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.81,0:53:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 我们错了 我们不敢了\N{\ren}Big brother, we were wrong, we're so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.91,0:53:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,狗子 我听不到 再说\N{\ren}Gouzi! Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.57,0:53:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,狗子 快呀 承认错呀 说呀\N{\ren}Gouzi, say you're sorry! Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.81,0:53:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快说啊 狗子\N{\ren}Come on, Gouzi...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.64,0:53:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 我们错了\N{\ren}Big brother, we're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.67,0:53:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 他们知道错了\N{\ren}Big brother, they know they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.57,0:53:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\ren}Have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从前我做官的时候\N{\ren}When I was still a civil servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.61,0:53:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在街上看见一个捕快\N{\ren}I saw a soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.61,0:53:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住一个穷人 见着就打\N{\ren}beating a peasant on the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.87,0:53:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,打得遍体鳞伤 浑身是血\N{\ren}...until the man was covered with his own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.24,0:53:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何理由\N{\ren}There was no reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.94,0:53:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为他穷\N{\ren}except that the man was poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.97,0:54:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而这个穷人 并没有怨言\N{\ren}But the poor man never retaliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.51,0:54:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好像一切都是天公地道的\N{\ren}He accepted it as part of his lot in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.34,0:54:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,从那天我就发誓\N{\ren}I promised myself that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.14,0:54:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我作主\N{\ren}I would never allow...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.74,0:54:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事就决不能再发生\N{\ren}something like that to happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.27,0:54:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们投军\N{\ren}You joined the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.11,0:54:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了不让别人欺负\N{\ren}because you don't want to be bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.27,0:54:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我告诉你\N{\ren}Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.77,0:54:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不光你们\N{\ren}not only you but everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.77,0:54:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,全天下的百姓都不能让人欺负\N{\ren}men and women alike should be free from oppression!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.94,0:54:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的是这样的大事\N{\ren}That's what we're fighting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.77,0:54:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,直到那一天\N{\ren}That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.07,0:54:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他才终于说出了他心里的未来\N{\ren}he finally revealed his dream for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.67,0:54:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我\N{\ren}He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.11,0:54:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,以前不做是时候不到\N{\ren}he waited because he was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.31,0:54:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怕我们不懂\N{\ren}we wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.84,0:54:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\ren}But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.44,0:54:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\ren}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.27,0:54:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人轮到你杀吗\N{\ren}Don't you touch my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.97,0:54:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\ren}Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.64,0:54:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.04,0:54:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\ren}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.04,0:54:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的命是谁的\N{\ren}Who do you owe your lives to?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.91,0:55:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁的\N{\ren}Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.37,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥的\N{\ren}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.81,0:55:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我娘该怎么说\N{\ren}What will you tell my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.74,0:55:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛闭起来\N{\ren}Closes your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.87,0:55:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很快\N{\ren}I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.84,0:55:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳哥 你跟我娘该怎么说\N{\ren}Brother Jiang... What will you tell my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.27,0:55:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我娘\N{\ren}Don't tell my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.47,0:55:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我能为这个未来而死\N{\ren}How I wish I could sacrifice my life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.81,0:55:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那该有多好\N{\ren}for this future of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.04,0:55:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为\N{\ren}I used to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.94,0:55:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,打仗抢东西才会杀人\N{\ren}we only kill to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.97,0:55:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才明白\N{\ren}Now I see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.01,0:56:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,心变好了也要杀人\N{\ren}we must also kill in order to do good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.24,0:56:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应你尽快结束这场战争\N{\ren}We must end this war in 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.87,0:56:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三个月打下苏州\N{\ren}We must take Suzhou!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.54,0:56:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,唷 孤子\N{\ren}Look! The abandoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.11,0:56:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么跟庞青云一样\N{\ren}You're behaving like Pang,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.24,0:56:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,顾头不顾腚啊\N{\ren}too ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.14,0:56:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,几千人就想打苏州 不自量力\N{\ren}Thinks he can take Suzhou with a few thousand men?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.54,0:56:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是替陈公着想\N{\ren}I'm worried for you, Lord Chen
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.91,0:56:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,断了根 又无粮草\N{\ren}With no supplies or reinforcements...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.77,0:56:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,死定了\N{\ren}He's dead for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.17,0:56:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,胜负往往在瞬息万变之中\N{\ren}There's a fine line between winning and losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.37,0:56:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果在这儿 连下去\N{\ren}If I add the right piece... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.61,0:56:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云在朝廷一步登天\N{\ren}Pang might just climb to the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.41,0:56:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候\N{\ren}with his next victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.51,0:56:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让庞青云连回去吗\N{\ren}Do you think I'd let Pang return to the fold?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.57,0:57:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,弃子\N{\ren}Leaving him stranded...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.17,0:57:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对大家都有好处\N{\ren}benefits everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.11,0:57:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州城 一年后\N{\ren}"Suzhou City, One Year Later"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.24,0:57:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都在干什么\N{\ren}What's keeping all of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.31,0:57:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们再不来 我就卸了你们的腿\N{\ren}Come get me now or I'll break your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.21,0:58:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州城已成死局\N{\ren}Suzhou is at an impasse;
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.44,0:58:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,攻守都得死\N{\ren}both sides will starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.54,0:58:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营就在城外等着呢\N{\ren}The Kui army are waiting to swoop like vultures!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.14,0:58:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要赌到什么时候\N{\ren}How much longer can you afford to gamble?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.67,0:58:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,猪倌\N{\ren}Butcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.14,0:58:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我唱首歌吧\N{\ren}...sing me a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.27,0:58:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听说\N{\ren}I heard that...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.57,0:58:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听说有个叫耶稣的先生\N{\ren}there is a man named Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.31,0:58:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每天中午\N{\ren}Each day at noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.37,0:58:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都给苏州城姓黄的\N{\ren}He gives the Taiping general Huang in Suzhou...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.54,0:58:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,五张大饼 两口肥猪\N{\ren}5 loaves of bread and 2 fat pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.41,0:58:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,随便就随便那么一分\N{\ren}He would then divide the food casually...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.11,0:58:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就能让五千多个人\N{\ren}and somehow he feeds all 5000 people...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.01,0:58:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,全都吃饱了\N{\ren}Everyone is fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.84,0:59:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,饼怎么分就是分不完\N{\ren}Their bread never runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.31,0:59:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,猪 猪每天都在下崽儿\N{\ren}And new piglets are being born everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.31,0:59:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\ren}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.54,0:59:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\ren}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.14,0:59:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我进城杀了黄文金\N{\ren}I'll steal into the city and kill Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.21,0:59:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去的人没一个活着回来\N{\ren}Those who tried never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.24,0:59:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不许你们去牺牲\N{\ren}I won't put more lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.81,0:59:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找狄公\N{\ren}I'll go ask Lord Di...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.27,0:59:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要粮要炮\N{\ren}for food and weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.64,1:00:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们攻打苏州 已经是违抗军令\N{\ren}But we've defied their orders by attacking Suzhou.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.70,1:00:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他们还有用\N{\ren}I'm still of some use to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.44,1:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,两位回去吧\N{\ren}Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.40,1:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给我粮 我就能拿下苏州\N{\ren}Give me provisions and I'll seize Suzhou!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.80,1:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兵只能战死 不能饿死\N{\ren}My men may die in battles but not from hunger!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.60,1:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你啦\N{\ren}Please, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.94,1:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大人说啦 他根本不知道苏州在打仗\N{\ren}My lord says he didn't know Suzhou was at war.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.57,1:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,去魁字营\N{\ren}To the Kui army!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.70,1:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 不能求他们\N{\ren}We can't go begging to them!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.64,1:01:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想不通你就回去\N{\ren}Then I will go alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.17,1:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快 快走\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.14,1:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.14,1:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.70,1:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来 抓住\N{\ren}Take my hand!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.97,1:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想爬进城\N{\ren}They tried to steal into the city;
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.80,1:01:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都说城里有吃的\N{\ren}they all said there was food inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.60,1:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我得进去\N{\ren}I must go in for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.07,1:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给我粮食 枪炮\N{\ren}Give me provisions and weapons...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.07,1:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们作笔交易\N{\ren}I'll make you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.64,1:02:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不给你\N{\ren}I don't need that -
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.94,1:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州城也是我的\N{\ren}Suzhou is already mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.87,1:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是\N{\ren}I'm talking about...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.20,1:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,南京\N{\ren}Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.70,1:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,仗我打 城我攻 人我死\N{\ren}My men do the fighting and the dying!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.50,1:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营只要站在后边作作样子\N{\ren}All you have to do is stand behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.30,1:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,南京 一人一半\N{\ren}We divide Nanking between us;
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.50,1:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们携手进城\N{\ren}we enter the city together...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.64,1:03:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你甘心一辈子\N{\ren}unless you want to be under.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.84,1:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,被那三个老头儿踩在脚下\N{\ren}the power of those three old men forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.10,1:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定要先打下南京\N{\ren}We must capture Nanking...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.07,1:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让朝廷知道打南京跟何魁无关\N{\ren}before the Kui army arrives to take credit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.60,1:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我们只有十天粮\N{\ren}But we only have 10 days' supplies.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.34,1:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要快\N{\ren}We act quickly
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.94,1:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,两天 拿下苏州\N{\ren}We capture Suzhou within 2 days!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.00,1:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老天真好\N{\ren}The heavens are good to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.34,1:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候把你送过来\N{\ren}sending you to me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.50,1:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,保平安的\N{\ren}It can protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.50,1:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,卯时 看不到城里的红烟\N{\ren}If you don't see a red flare by dawn from inside the city...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.14,1:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人会带你走\N{\ren}my men will take you to safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.94,1:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跟大哥 午阳他们说\N{\ren}Tell big brother and Wu-Yang that...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.84,1:04:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎想当英雄\N{\ren}Er-Hu wanted to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.54,1:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,将军回来了\N{\ren}General Pang is back!...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.60,1:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,庞将军 粮食已经送来了\N{\ren}Sir, the provisions have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.37,1:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎将军进城了\N{\ren}General Zhao has entered the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.54,1:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,说卯时看见红烟\N{\ren}He said if we see a red flare by dawn...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.44,1:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就代表他成功了\N{\ren}it means he has succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.10,1:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟 跟你要的货带了吗\N{\ren}My friend, did you bring the goods?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.07,1:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都说城里有粮食\N{\ren}They say we have food in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.47,1:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再这么耗下去 就得人吃人\N{\ren}But we may start eating each other soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.34,1:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过兄弟们 吃饱穿暖\N{\ren}I promised they would be clothed and fed...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.37,1:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三年打完仗回家享福\N{\ren}and could go home within 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.87,1:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在五年了\N{\ren}It's been 5 years now...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.44,1:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,明天卯时 攻城\N{\ren}We attack at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.37,1:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嫂子\N{\ren}Lian.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.54,1:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢看人的脸\N{\ren}I like to study different faces...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.34,1:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州被围\N{\ren}but I haven't seen a new face...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.44,1:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经一年没见过生人了\N{\ren}since Suzhou came under siege a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.74,1:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这次送鸦片的是个陌生人\N{\ren}I hear the opium dealer is a new face
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.97,1:10:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西 我已经戒了\N{\ren}but I don't use opium anymore -
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.44,1:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,它只能止痛\N{\ren}it only eases the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.74,1:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子的坟墓就在城外的小树林里\N{\ren}My wife's grave is just outside the city in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.00,1:10:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去看\N{\ren}I long to see her...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.04,1:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,却不能看\N{\ren}but can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.27,1:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你能明白一个囚徒的心思吗\N{\ren}Do you know what it's like to be a prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.94,1:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州城就像一个大牢 已经很久了\N{\ren}Suzhou has become one big prison...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.67,1:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想出 但出不去\N{\ren}I can't get out...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.10,1:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想进 也进不来\N{\ren}you can't get in either...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.17,1:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,除非\N{\ren}unless...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你进来\N{\ren}I let you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.14,1:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的同乡\N{\ren}Remember Shi?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.57,1:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你投了清 他跟了我\N{\ren}You joined the Qing army, he followed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.50,1:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.50,1:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大人 卯时已过\N{\ren}Sir... it's past dawn
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.54,1:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,备马\N{\ren}Prepare the horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.37,1:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,送赵夫人\N{\ren}Escort Lady Zhao away.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.37,1:11:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎留下话\N{\ren}Er-hu said that...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.27,1:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说他要当英雄\N{\ren}he wanted to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.14,1:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能活下来\N{\ren}If I survive, I will...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.07,1:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,娶你\N{\ren}marry you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.27,1:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有四千饿疯了的士兵\N{\ren}4,000 soldiers are outside crazed with starvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.24,1:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我\N{\ren}If you kill me...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.07,1:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州会变成鬼城 所有的人都要死\N{\ren}you will all die in a blood bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.20,1:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也四千士兵\N{\ren}I too have 4,000 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.20,1:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将会为守住苏州城每一寸土地\N{\ren}They'll defend every inch of the city...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.27,1:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,流尽最后一滴血\N{\ren}to their last drop of blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.44,1:12:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,都退下\N{\ren}Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.57,1:12:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,卸下武器\N{\ren}Lay down your arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.84,1:13:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧\N{\ren}Please surrender!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.60,1:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,十一年前\N{\ren}11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.97,1:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我卖了祖业 关了生意\N{\ren}I closed my business and sold everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.04,1:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,投了太平\N{\ren}to join the Taiping rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.72,1:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,从那天起\N{\ren}From that day on...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.12,1:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,投降这两个字\N{\ren}the word "surrender"...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.79,1:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就永远的消失了\N{\ren}no longer existed for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.15,1:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不死\N{\ren}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.22,1:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州城这个大牢里的人\N{\ren}the people of Suzhou City...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.95,1:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就出不去\N{\ren}will never be free.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.25,1:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让士兵回家务农\N{\ren}Spare my soldiers... let them go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.25,1:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要羞辱城里的百姓\N{\ren}Don't make the civilians suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.15,1:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安心\N{\ren}May you...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.99,1:14:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上路\N{\ren}go in peace!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.29,1:15:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,预备\N{\ren}Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.25,1:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎 二虎\N{\ren}Er-Hu... Er-Hu...!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.09,1:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赵二虎\N{\ren}Zhao Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.19,1:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见赵二虎\N{\ren}I want to see Zhao Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.32,1:18:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,馒头\N{\ren}We want bread! Bread!...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.55,1:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们真的要收编他们啊\N{\ren}Are we going to conscript them?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.05,1:18:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会同意的\N{\ren}They will never agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.29,1:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,四千个俘虏 四千张嘴\N{\ren}There are 4,000 captives.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.15,1:18:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你想动用多少军粮喂饱他们\N{\ren}How much of our food will you give them?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.62,1:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.29,1:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们活路\N{\ren}They surrendered only because...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.29,1:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们开城投降的条件\N{\ren}I promised to let them live.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.19,1:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州的粮仓早就空了\N{\ren}The city's granaries are empty, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.25,1:18:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的粮食只有十天\N{\ren}we have only a 10-day-supply of food.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.89,1:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要留着打南京\N{\ren}We must save it for Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.32,1:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么打南京啊\N{\ren}Nanking?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.89,1:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 什么打南京啊\N{\ren}Are we attacking Nanking?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.89,1:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营集结完毕\N{\ren}The Kui army decamped yesterday;
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.19,1:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都会攻打南京\N{\ren}they will attack Nanking at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.99,1:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不识字\N{\ren}I can't read!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.92,1:18:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要给我看 告诉我 哪来的粮食\N{\ren}Just tell me where the supplies are from?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.22,1:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哪来的\N{\ren}Where?!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.19,1:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营\N{\ren}The Kui army.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.35,1:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要跟他们交易啊\N{\ren}How could you make a deal with He Kui?!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.69,1:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这四千人拒绝收编\N{\ren}These solders will never join our army.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.95,1:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,打南京\N{\ren}If we attack Nanking...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.05,1:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这苏州城就是空城\N{\ren}Suzhou will be defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.55,1:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心把苏州城交给他们吗\N{\ren}Can you leave the city in their hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.75,1:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 你听我说好不好 你听我说\N{\ren}- Listen to me! - No, you listen!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.45,1:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这四千人拿起枪就是兵\N{\ren}These soldiers are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.45,1:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,馒头 馒头\N{\ren}We want bread! Bread!...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.15,1:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,开城门\N{\ren}Open the stores!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.59,1:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给我发粮\N{\ren}Give me what I need.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.55,1:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.25,1:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang Qing-Yun!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.32,1:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我早知道你是什么人\N{\ren}I knew you were a liar!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.79,1:19:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这馒头\N{\ren}This bread...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.32,1:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,本来是我们兄弟要吃的\N{\ren}was meant for our brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.12,1:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要分一半给这四千人\N{\ren}But you want to give half to the captives...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.65,1:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再分一半给城里的百姓\N{\ren}and then the other half to the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.55,1:19:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们围城围了九个月\N{\ren}Our brothers have fought for 9 months...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.72,1:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了九个月\N{\ren}and starved for 9 months!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.32,1:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这馒头\N{\ren}You tell me...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.35,1:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是给我们还是他们\N{\ren}Who should get this bread, them or us?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.95,1:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管\N{\ren}I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.69,1:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,发粮\N{\ren}Give them food!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.55,1:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,发 发\N{\ren}Now!!!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.32,1:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就一顿\N{\ren}Let them eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.22,1:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们吃饱\N{\ren}It's their last meal
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.15,1:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过要让他们活着\N{\ren}But I promised to spare their lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.72,1:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,兵不厌诈 这是战争\N{\ren}Winning is all that matters in war!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.79,1:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人无信就是畜生\N{\ren}A man who breaks his word is a beast!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.29,1:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,二哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.62,1:20:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥是对的\N{\ren}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.75,1:20:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\ren}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.79,1:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥是对的\N{\ren}He's right
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.62,1:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给我让开\N{\ren}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.82,1:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥是对的\N{\ren}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.22,1:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 放开\N{\ren}Let me go!...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.92,1:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我 我答应过要让他们活着\N{\ren}Let me go! I promised to spare their lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.40,1:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,备箭\N{\ren}Archers!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.63,1:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\ren}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.73,1:22:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能杀\N{\ren}Don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.50,1:22:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.16,1:22:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.53,1:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.63,1:22:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.03,1:22:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不能杀 不能杀\N{\ren}Don't kill them! Don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.26,1:22:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.70,1:22:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.20,1:22:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再放\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.03,1:24:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那天以后\N{\ren}From that day on...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.33,1:24:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,二哥再也没和我说过一句话\N{\ren}Er-Hu never said another word to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.76,1:24:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我难过 可是\N{\ren}It hurts, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.40,1:24:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥是对的\N{\ren}big brother was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.50,1:26:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,回家啦\N{\ren}Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.90,1:26:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁跟我\N{\ren}Who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.30,1:26:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎 你不能走\N{\ren}Er-Hu, you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.36,1:26:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要去打南京呢\N{\ren}We still have to take Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.33,1:26:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我继续看你杀那些手无寸铁的人\N{\ren}What for? To kill more defenseless people?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.10,1:26:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是兵\N{\ren}They were soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.70,1:26:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,投降了\N{\ren}They surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.70,1:26:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还是兵\N{\ren}They were still soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.10,1:27:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得过去你跟我们讲什么\N{\ren}Do you remember what you said to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.06,1:27:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你要找个地方\N{\ren}You said everyone deserves...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.90,1:27:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让老百姓不会因为穷就挨打\N{\ren}to be free even the poor!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.13,1:27:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在做了什么\N{\ren}What have you done now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.73,1:27:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就在这里\N{\ren}You have ordered right here...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.46,1:27:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了四千个穷人 你知道吗\N{\ren}the massacre of 4,000 poor people?! You know that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.80,1:27:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是穷人 谁会去打仗\N{\ren}Only the poor are willing to go to war!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.23,1:27:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小顺子 小五子 小七子 哪个不是穷人\N{\ren}Which one of us weren't poor!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.10,1:27:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们是兵\N{\ren}Those men were soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.66,1:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是兵就会死\N{\ren}Soldiers are prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.60,1:27:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可南京城 上百万的是老百姓\N{\ren}But the millions in Nanking are just civilians.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.63,1:27:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁先进去就完了\N{\ren}If He Kui reaches them first, they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.93,1:27:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打南京 我需要你\N{\ren}I need your help to take Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.03,1:27:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要走\N{\ren}Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.23,1:27:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你一走可是兵变啊\N{\ren}If you go, it will be mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.63,1:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这山字营的兄弟就会自相残杀\N{\ren}The Shan brothers will turn on each other!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.16,1:27:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那后果\N{\ren}Think about the consequences!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.76,1:27:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逼我\N{\ren}Don't force my hand!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.10,1:27:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谁敢动二哥 我跟他拼了\N{\ren}I'll kill anyone who touches Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.80,1:28:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,二哥 千万不可以走\N{\ren}Brother, you must not leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.73,1:28:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你走了 我们这个家就真的没了\N{\ren}If you leave now... ours pledge will be broken
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.83,1:28:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎\N{\ren}Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.30,1:28:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁的兵已经出发了\N{\ren}The Kui army has already left.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.60,1:28:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们再不走就来不及了\N{\ren}We must leave now or we'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.00,1:28:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\ren}I promise you...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.46,1:28:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打完南京\N{\ren}after Nanking...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.33,1:28:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会放下刀\N{\ren}there'll be peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.50,1:28:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,将来你会知道\N{\ren}One day you'll see that...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.10,1:28:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天的决定是对的\N{\ren}my decisions today were right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.46,1:28:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.76,1:28:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,进南京 我看着你\N{\ren}I'll be watching you in Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.50,1:28:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你对 我跪还你\N{\ren}If you're right, I'll kneel before you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.96,1:28:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你错 我就杀了你\N{\ren}But if you're wrong, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.73,1:29:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.40,1:29:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,俺\N{\ren}We...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.70,1:29:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,赵二虎 庞青云\N{\ren}Zhao Er-Hu... Pang Qing-Yun...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.23,1:29:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,姜午阳 弟兄三人\N{\ren}Jiang Wu-Yang... three brothers as one...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.00,1:29:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,杀\N{\ren}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.26,1:29:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,礼花满天 南京攻陷\N{\ren}Victory is ours, Nanking is ours!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.20,1:29:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,礼炮一响 太后吉祥\N{\ren}Long live the Empress Dowager!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.53,1:29:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,南京 降城后一个月\N{\ren}One month after the capture of Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.52,1:30:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,安心上路\N{\ren}Go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.92,1:30:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发过誓\N{\ren}We swore an oath...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.25,1:30:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一辈子都是山字营的人\N{\ren}to remain loyal to the Shan regiment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.92,1:30:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这世界上 有人挨饿被欺负\N{\ren}As long as there is hunger, oppression...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.29,1:30:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有人是非不分\N{\ren}and injustice...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.79,1:30:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们山字营永远都在\N{\ren}the Shan regiment will fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.82,1:30:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,发军饷\N{\ren}Dole out the wages!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.02,1:31:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,张文方 五两\N{\ren}Zhang Wen-Fang, 5 taels.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.92,1:31:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,王小三\N{\ren}Wang Xiao-San...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.62,1:31:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎 你知不知道你在做什么\N{\ren}Er-Hu, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.95,1:31:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,私分朝廷军饷是重罪\N{\ren}The money belongs to the imperial coffers!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.42,1:31:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进了南京之后 有一半是军饷\N{\ren}We agreed to take Nanking and give half of the spoils to our men.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.12,1:31:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不发 我帮你发\N{\ren}If you won't do it! I will!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.82,1:31:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要记住\N{\ren}Remember!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.89,1:31:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,军队里面就只有一个头\N{\ren}The Shan regiment has only one leader!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.92,1:31:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这个头 就是庞大人庞将军\N{\ren}And that's General Pang!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.69,1:31:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还不赶快谢谢他\N{\ren}Show him your gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.15,1:31:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢庞大人\N{\ren}Thank you General!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.55,1:31:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再说\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.62,1:31:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢庞大人\N{\ren}Thank you General!!!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.39,1:31:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,继续发钱\N{\ren}Back to the wages...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.95,1:31:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,王小三 三两四钱\N{\ren}Wang Xiao-San, 3 taels 4 mace.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.72,1:31:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,王郎 四两\N{\ren}Wang Long, 4 taels
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.25,1:31:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,何大人\N{\ren}My lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.69,1:32:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,打南京 你给他粮\N{\ren}He needed your help to take Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.99,1:32:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,进了南京 你成要饭的了\N{\ren}Now you're at his mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.79,1:32:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早要杀了他\N{\ren}I will kill him eventually!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.59,1:32:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一步慢 步步慢\N{\ren}You're always a step behind
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.59,1:32:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太后要他做两江总督\N{\ren}The Empress is making him Governor of Jiangsu.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.75,1:32:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样\N{\ren}So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.32,1:32:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁 这回我帮不了你啦\N{\ren}He Kiu, even I can't help you this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.02,1:32:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们把赵二虎给拉过来\N{\ren}We just need to get Zhao Er-Hu on our side...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.72,1:32:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,两江总督 他肯定做不长\N{\ren}and Pang's downfall is ensured!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.09,1:32:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,赵二虎 庞青云 姜午阳\N{\ren}Zhao Er-Hu... Pang Qing-Yun... Jiang Wu-Yang...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.09,1:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弟兄三人\N{\ren}three brothers as one...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.79,1:32:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喝酒 喝\N{\ren}Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.65,1:32:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,歃血为盟神灵鉴\N{\ren}Heaven and earth be our witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.82,1:32:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,义字当先对地天\N{\ren}We take a blood oath, pledge our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.12,1:33:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不求同生求同死\N{\ren}We were born apart but die as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.15,1:33:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,祸福共当\N{\ren}Loyalty through good times...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.79,1:33:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,肝胆悬\N{\ren}and bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.85,1:34:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赵大人 仗是你打的\N{\ren}General Zhao, you did the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.42,1:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,功劳让别人独吞\N{\ren}but he took the credit.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.99,1:34:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你恨吗\N{\ren}How can you live with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.65,1:34:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样\N{\ren}So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.55,1:34:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这戏里唱的是兄弟情\N{\ren}This opera is about brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.65,1:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,既是兄弟 他为什么把你锁进祠堂\N{\ren}He's your brother, yet he had you in chains?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.85,1:34:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让你背信弃义 任天下人耻笑\N{\ren}He forced you to break your word and made a fool out of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.49,1:34:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,割了这把草\N{\ren}Make him pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.22,1:34:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你我联手 一了百了 共用南京\N{\ren}If we join forces and Nanking can be ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.32,1:34:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想吧 赵大人\N{\ren}Give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.65,1:34:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,何将军是在为你盘算\N{\ren}General He is only thinking of your future.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.89,1:34:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\ren}Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.25,1:35:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打的好\N{\ren}Revenge is sweet!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.45,1:35:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他抽你两鞭子的仇好报\N{\ren}Shallow wounds heal...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.52,1:35:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可你心里的恨难解\N{\ren}but deep wounds fester.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.39,1:35:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,赵大人 慢慢想 不急\N{\ren}General Zhao, take your time to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.42,1:35:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,何大人\N{\ren}General He.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.79,1:36:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是在想\N{\ren}You must be wondering...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.82,1:36:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从宫门外走到这儿需要多久\N{\ren}how long it takes to get from the gates to here?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.72,1:37:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻时候 我头一次站在宫门外\N{\ren}I had the same thought the first time...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.35,1:37:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也是这么想啊\N{\ren}I stood outside the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.52,1:37:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可等真的走到这儿\N{\ren}By the time I reached this far...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.62,1:37:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是两鬓斑白\N{\ren}my hair had already turned gray
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.92,1:37:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,用了整整三十年了\N{\ren}it took me 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.32,1:37:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜啊 走不动啦\N{\ren}Now I'm too old to walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.89,1:37:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小李子\N{\ren}Li Lianying.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.49,1:37:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太后说 你还年轻\N{\ren}The Empress said your youth is an asset;
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.42,1:37:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,君臣相伴会长久\N{\ren}you will serve us for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.89,1:37:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,太后还说 收复南京\N{\ren}The Empress also said.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.35,1:37:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云劳苦功高\N{\ren}Pang should be commended for the capture of Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.65,1:37:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,赏黄马褂一件\N{\ren}He will receive the Golden Robes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.99,1:37:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,加封两江总督 钦此\N{\ren}and appointed Governor of Jiangsu!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.09,1:37:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快谢\N{\ren}Show your gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.49,1:38:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,臣 庞青云\N{\ren}Your servant Pang requests that...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.85,1:38:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,启奏太后免除两江辖区三年赋税\N{\ren}the people of Jiangsu be exempt from 3 years of taxes
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.82,1:38:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,修生养民\N{\ren}to recover from the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.89,1:38:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,准奏\N{\ren}Request granted!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.52,1:38:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢太后\N{\ren}Thank you your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.95,1:38:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州杀人 南京活人\N{\ren}You're responsible for the Suzhou massacre...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.42,1:38:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人是君子豹变\N{\ren}yet you saved the people of Nanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.49,1:38:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是辅国良臣啊\N{\ren}Lord Pang, you're surely adaptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.12,1:38:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为庞大人和朝廷不属任何派系\N{\ren}The Empress favors Lord Pang because
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.42,1:38:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,才得太后的垂青\N{\ren}he does not belong to any fractions.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.99,1:38:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,南京是给了你\N{\ren}Nanking may be yours,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.92,1:38:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可姜大人气得是卧病南方\N{\ren}But you've offended Lord Jiang and He Kui along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.32,1:38:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁又蠢蠢欲动\N{\ren}Now, without allies...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.62,1:38:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你 镇得住吗\N{\ren}how long do you think you'll last?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.79,1:38:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人 我翻了翻黄历\N{\ren}Lord Pang, I checked the lunar calendar.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.52,1:38:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,四月初八午时上任\N{\ren}The 8th day of the 4th month...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.52,1:38:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,利国利民 利己\N{\ren}will be the most auspicious time for your inauguration
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.79,1:39:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大吉\N{\ren}...and for all.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.09,1:39:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要想有所作为\N{\ren}Before you can do good...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.95,1:39:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人 你得好好活着\N{\ren}Lord Pang, you must look after yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.09,1:39:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好好活着\N{\ren}You must look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.29,1:39:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我有公务在身 告辞了\N{\ren}I must leave now, My lords.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.35,1:39:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,叛乱虽平\N{\ren}The unrest has subsided,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.95,1:39:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可地方督府个个手握重兵\N{\ren}but the local militias wield too much power.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.82,1:39:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人 这太后不放心\N{\ren}Lord Pang, the Empress is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.19,1:39:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,山字营带头裁军\N{\ren}The Shan regiment will be the first to disband.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.29,1:39:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Good!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.59,1:39:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人跟军队做了了断\N{\ren}Once you sever your old ties...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.52,1:39:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,便可专心履行你的总督的事务啦\N{\ren}you can devote yourself to your duties as governor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.72,1:39:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你兄弟赵二虎 在苏州说要走\N{\ren}Your brother Zhao Er-Hu threatened to desert the army in Suzhou.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.89,1:39:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,结果呢\N{\ren}He almost created...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.82,1:39:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一呼百应\N{\ren}a mutiny there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.79,1:39:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在南京 又私分朝廷军饷\N{\ren}In Nanking, he doled out funds meant for the royal coffers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.75,1:39:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你山字营姓赵啊\N{\ren}Does he own your regiment?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.22,1:40:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大人 危险\N{\ren}Be careful, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.95,1:40:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我这一生 如履薄冰\N{\ren}I've walked on thin ice my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.89,1:40:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我能走到对岸吗\N{\ren}Do you think I can safely cross over?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.32,1:41:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\ren}You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.32,1:41:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我醒了\N{\ren}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.22,1:41:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可能真的是他们对的\N{\ren}Perhaps they're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.99,1:41:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,南京\N{\ren}Nanking...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.82,1:41:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不需要我这种人\N{\ren}doesn't need someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.79,1:41:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家\N{\ren}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.52,1:41:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意吗\N{\ren}Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.69,1:41:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要了\N{\ren}I don't need this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.42,1:41:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\ren}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.35,1:41:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷 出大事了\N{\ren}Bad news, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.92,1:41:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,魁字营要反 何魁要杀庞大人\N{\ren}He Kui plans to assassinate Lord Pang!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.25,1:42:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\ren}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.72,1:42:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷\N{\ren}General Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.65,1:42:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.69,1:42:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷\N{\ren}General Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.42,1:42:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.32,1:42:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,二爷\N{\ren}General Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.55,1:42:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥呢\N{\ren}Where's he?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.92,1:42:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人去了京城 还没回来\N{\ren}Lord Pang has not returned from the imperial court.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.75,1:42:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,您决定了\N{\ren}Decided?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.92,1:42:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去了\N{\ren}Then I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.99,1:42:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,三爷\N{\ren}General Jiang.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.92,1:42:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,三爷\N{\ren}General Jiang.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.65,1:42:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁\N{\ren}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.99,1:42:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,京城调来的御林军\N{\ren}Guards sent by the imperial court.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.42,1:42:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,红色那块桌布 一会儿赶快给我铺上\N{\ren}Cover that table with the red cloth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.12,1:42:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,偏厅偏厅 一会儿还有这个\N{\ren}Move these vases as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.72,1:42:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧的\N{\ren}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.15,1:42:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,三爷 怎么 有客人\N{\ren}Brother Wu Yang You have guests coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.12,1:43:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,您不知道 庞大人请赵大人吃饭\N{\ren}General Pang has invited General Zhao to dine.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.85,1:43:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们和好了\N{\ren}They've reconciled!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.22,1:43:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥回来了\N{\ren}Is big brother home?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.79,1:43:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说是下午就回来\N{\ren}He should return by the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.39,1:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这府上的侍卫全换人了\N{\ren}why have they replaced all the guards?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.85,1:43:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,赵将军 慢走\N{\ren}General Zhao, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.35,1:43:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赵将军\N{\ren}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.59,1:43:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才收到密报 庞大人要做两江总督\N{\ren}We received news that...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.45,1:43:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁要兵变\N{\ren}He Kui plans to assassinate Lord Pang.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.99,1:43:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大人进不了城\N{\ren}He must not return to the city now
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.39,1:43:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,约你到城外江浦镇商量对策\N{\ren}he asked you to meet him at Jianpu.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.72,1:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,让午阳带人 到江浦镇集合\N{\ren}Tell Wu-Yang to bring the others and meet us there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.65,1:43:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳\N{\ren}Wu-Yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.92,1:43:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我找二哥\N{\ren}Where's Er-Hu?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.05,1:43:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,二哥\N{\ren}He...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.59,1:43:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去找庞大哥了\N{\ren}went to see Brother Pang.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.79,1:44:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你有事瞒我\N{\ren}You're up to something!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.72,1:44:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,院子里多了很多生人\N{\ren}What's with all those new guards?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.52,1:45:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要动二哥\N{\ren}You're going to kill Er-Hu...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.02,1:45:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了嫂子\N{\ren}all because of Lian?!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.99,1:45:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了投名状\N{\ren}Have you forgotten our pledge?!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.55,1:45:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,二哥什么时候到\N{\ren}When will Er-Hu arrive?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.72,1:45:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给我最后时限\N{\ren}Tell me when!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.69,1:45:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亥时\N{\ren}Nightfall...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.32,1:45:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亥时二虎到\N{\ren}He'll be here by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.29,1:45:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你等我\N{\ren}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.85,1:46:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你吓了我一跳\N{\ren}You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.15,1:46:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嫂子 午阳来与你告别\N{\ren}Lian, I'm here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.82,1:46:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你要走吗\N{\ren}Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.49,1:46:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我送你\N{\ren}No, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.82,1:46:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我去哪儿\N{\ren}But where to?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.05,1:46:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等二虎回来呢\N{\ren}I'm waiting for Er-Hu...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.65,1:46:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚给他做了晚饭\N{\ren}I've just prepared dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.59,1:46:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥为了你 要杀二哥\N{\ren}Big brother is going to kill Er-Hu over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.59,1:46:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 不会的\N{\ren}No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.32,1:46:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你下来\N{\ren}Come down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.45,1:46:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.12,1:46:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这个纱帘弄好\N{\ren}I have to finish draping this frame.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.29,1:46:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过这么好看的纱帘吗\N{\ren}Have you ever seen such beautiful fabric?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.19,1:46:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我都十几年没见过这么好看的纱帘了\N{\ren}I haven't seen one in years.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.85,1:46:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天在铺里 还看见一个红色的\N{\ren}I saw the red one in a shop yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.45,1:47:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要绿的 也想要红的\N{\ren}but I also wanted the green one.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.05,1:47:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我问二虎怎么办呢\N{\ren}I asked Er-Hu what to do
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.02,1:47:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,二虎说\N{\ren}He said...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.09,1:47:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今年绿的 明年红的\N{\ren}green for this year and red for the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.82,1:47:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我明年就二十九岁了\N{\ren}I'll be 29 next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.15,1:47:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,打了十四年仗\N{\ren}I lived through 14 years of war...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.79,1:47:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没饿死 也没被砍死\N{\ren}didn't starve to death or get killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.79,1:47:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我命大\N{\ren}I've been lucky!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.52,1:47:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明年还要挂红色的纱帘\N{\ren}I still have to hang the red curtain next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.99,1:47:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我明年还要挂红色的纱帘\N{\ren}I still have to hang the red curtain next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.62,1:47:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下来\N{\ren}Come down!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.99,1:47:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会杀我的 我不准你杀我\N{\ren}You wouldn't kill me... I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.55,1:47:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我好不容易活到现在\N{\ren}It wasn't easy for me to survive!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.09,1:47:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀死我\N{\ren}Why must you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.75,1:47:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不杀你 怎么救二哥\N{\ren}If I don't kill you... how will I save Er-Hu?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.92,1:47:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我 就能救二哥吗\N{\ren}Can you really save him by killing me?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.52,1:47:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\ren}I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.85,1:47:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只能这么做\N{\ren}but it's all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.52,1:47:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你从小就跟着我\N{\ren}I watched you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.62,1:47:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会的 你不会的\N{\ren}You wouldn't do it... You won't!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.52,1:48:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳 你不会忍心杀我的\N{\ren}I know you can't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.19,1:48:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会的\N{\ren}You wouldn't do it...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.12,1:48:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,外人乱我兄弟者\N{\ren}Anyone who harms our brothers...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.05,1:48:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会杀我的\N{\ren}You can't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.82,1:48:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,视投名状\N{\ren}must be...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.39,1:48:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀之\N{\ren}killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.79,1:48:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前\N{\ren}5 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.22,1:48:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一百零八个人 从一个小村子出来\N{\ren}108 men left their village to join the army...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.05,1:48:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,打仗拼命就为了一口饭吃\N{\ren}risking their lives for a little food.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.12,1:48:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是山字营最早的兄弟\N{\ren}They were the first to join the Shan army
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.19,1:48:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,领头的就是我们三个\N{\ren}The three of us were their leaders.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.99,1:49:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 我选了一个好地方送你走\N{\ren}Today, I found a good place to free you
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.25,1:49:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过\N{\ren}I told you...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.55,1:49:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天 你会明白我是对的\N{\ren}there will come a day when you'll see that I was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.95,1:49:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,每年这个时候 我都请你喝酒\N{\ren}Each year at this time, I'll drink with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.02,1:49:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你 我这一年都做了什么\N{\ren}I'll tell you what I've done in the past year.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.72,1:49:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才从京城回来\N{\ren}I just returned from the palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.55,1:49:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为咱们的百姓\N{\ren}The people of Jiangsu have been...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.05,1:50:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,免了三年的征税\N{\ren}spared from taxes for 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.19,1:50:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明年 明年我保证\N{\ren}Next year, I promise...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.49,1:50:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个百姓都吃得饱\N{\ren}no one will go hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.02,1:50:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你迟早会明白\N{\ren}You'll understand eventually
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.89,1:50:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小七 狗子\N{\ren}that Xiao-Qi and Gouzi...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.95,1:50:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,死的是值得的\N{\ren}didn't die in vain...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.19,1:50:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州的四千人\N{\ren}and the massacre of the 4000 captives...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.29,1:50:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,死的也是值得的\N{\ren}was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.25,1:50:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\ren}And you...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.65,1:50:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\ren}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.25,1:50:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也是值得的\N{\ren}You will not die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.22,1:50:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,苏州你要造反\N{\ren}You defied my orders in Suzhou.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.52,1:50:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以杀你\N{\ren}I could have killed you then,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.55,1:50:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我不舍得\N{\ren}but I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.15,1:50:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是现下朝廷\N{\ren}But now it's the imperial court...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.52,1:50:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,朝廷要你\N{\ren}that wants you dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.59,1:51:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,何魁\N{\ren}He Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.45,1:51:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说 我怎么办\N{\ren}What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.85,1:51:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你出来\N{\ren}Come out here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.09,1:51:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好兄弟 二虎\N{\ren}My brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.85,1:51:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安心上路\N{\ren}go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.99,1:51:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.59,1:51:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.42,1:51:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 你不用动二哥\N{\ren}Big brother, you don't need to kill Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.85,1:51:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.95,1:51:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.99,1:51:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用动二哥\N{\ren}you don't need to kill Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.32,1:51:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嫂子已经死了\N{\ren}Lian is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.92,1:52:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用动二哥了\N{\ren}You don't have to kill Er-Hu!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.45,1:52:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嫂子已经死了\N{\ren}Lian is already dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.82,1:52:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有杀二哥的理由了\N{\ren}no reason to kill Er-Hu now!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.22,1:52:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥\N{\ren}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.95,1:52:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嫂子已经死了\N{\ren}Lian is dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.52,1:53:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,圣主承天\N{\ren}The gods bless this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.42,1:53:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,作君师于下土\N{\ren}Joining the ranks of those that went before...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.65,1:53:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,良臣当国\N{\ren}a great servant to the empire.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.49,1:53:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,行政教于家邦\N{\ren}To lead by example and serve his people.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.89,1:53:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云荣任两江总督之庆典\N{\ren}The inauguration of Pang Qing-Yun as Governor of Jiangsu will take place...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.92,1:53:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,庚午四月初八午时\N{\ren}at noon on this day, the 8th of the 4th month.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.05,1:54:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一个篱笆得三个桩\N{\ren}A fence needs three pillars.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.32,1:54:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,姜大人不在 真是不热闹啊\N{\ren}It's not the same without Lord Jiang here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.69,1:54:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,已时三刻\N{\ren}A quarter to 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.39,1:55:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,停\N{\ren}Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.65,1:55:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟杀我兄弟者\N{\ren}A brother who harms another brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.95,1:55:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀之\N{\ren}must die!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.95,1:55:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟杀我兄弟者 必杀之\N{\ren}A brother who harms another brother must die.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.09,1:56:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,时辰到了\N{\ren}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.65,1:56:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你别再逼我\N{\ren}Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.09,1:56:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟杀我兄弟者\N{\ren}A brother who harms another brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.39,1:56:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,必杀之\N{\ren}must die!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.29,1:57:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,午阳\N{\ren}Wu-Yang!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.15,1:57:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你 别再打了\N{\ren}I beg you stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.19,1:57:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟杀我兄弟者 必杀之\N{\ren}A brother who harms another brother must die.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.85,1:58:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云\N{\ren}Pang Qing-Yun!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.15,1:58:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,庞青云是个人材\N{\ren}Pang has talent
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.85,1:59:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可不懂为官之道\N{\ren}but doesn't know how things work.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.28,1:59:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,南京是重镇\N{\ren}Nanking is of vital importance
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.92,1:59:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太后想安定天下\N{\ren}to the peace of the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.69,1:59:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎会倚仗一个外人\N{\ren}The Empress would never entrust it to an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.92,1:59:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜啊 这都是命\N{\ren}Pity... such is life.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.75,1:59:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,午时已到 鸣炮\N{\ren}Noon is here! Salute cannons, fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.95,2:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,投名状\N{\ren}Honor our pledge...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.49,2:01:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}now!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.65,2:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,刺庞者 姜午阳是也\N{\ren}I, Jiang Wu-Yang, killed Pang Qing-Yun!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.95,2:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在那一刻\N{\ren}At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.15,2:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我脑子里只有结拜时的一句话\N{\ren}My mind went back to the day we took the blood oath.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.72,2:01:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,生不同生 死必同死\N{\ren}We are born apart but we shall die as one.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.25,2:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一百八人 人无同面 面面峥嵘\N{\ren}Our origins are different...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.65,2:02:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一百八人 人合一心 心心皎洁\N{\ren}but our hearts act as one.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.32,2:02:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,乐必同乐 生不同生 死必同死\N{\ren}In good times and bad...in life and in death.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.05,2:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,既列名于天上 无贻笑于人间\N{\ren}We honor our pledge.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.96,2:02:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,报应分明 神天共察\N{\ren}With Heaven and earth as our witness.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.78,2:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿生生相会 世世相逢\N{\ren}We shall live and die as blood brothers...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.03,2:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,两江总督庞青云\N{\ren}Governor of Jiangsu, Pang Qing-Yun...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.98,2:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,于1870年7月26日遇刺身亡\N{\ren}was assassinated on the 26th of July, 1870.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.15,2:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刺客姜午阳两个月后被凌迟处死\N{\ren}His assassin Jiang Wu-Yang was executed 2 months later.

